Bundled theme attributions

Mark embeds TextMate/VS Code theme data from the projects below. The pinned
source revisions and per-theme file hashes are recorded in assets/themes/SOURCE.toml
in Mark's source tree:

  https://github.com/phongndo/mark/tree/main/assets/themes

- GitHub VS Code themes: https://github.com/primer/github-vscode-theme
- Shiki themes: https://github.com/shikijs/shiki
- Nordic: https://github.com/AlexvZyl/nordic.nvim
- Dark Molokai: https://github.com/nonylene/vscode-dark-molokai-theme
- Zenbones: https://github.com/zenbones-theme/zenbones.nvim
- Token: https://github.com/ThorstenRhau/token
- Gruvbox Material: https://github.com/sainnhe/gruvbox-material-vscode
- MFD: https://github.com/kungfusheep/mfd.nvim

The Nordic, Zenbones, and MFD files are modified adaptations that map upstream
Neovim/Vim highlight groups and palettes to TextMate scopes and VS Code
workbench color keys for use by Mark. Mark's adaptation is Copyright (c) 2026
Mark contributors.
